 actor best known for his role as lovable rogue Detective John "J.D." La Rue on the 80s television drama <it><series wordnetid="108457976" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../208/203208.xml">
Hill Street Blues</link></series>
.</it><p>

Martin was married twice, first to <link>
Claudia Martin</link> (1944-2001), who was actor/crooner <person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<artist wordnetid="109812338" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../603/151603.xml">
Dean Martin</link></artist>
</person>
